title: Most-viewed homes on Rightmove – in pictures
text:
Wellesbourne, Warwickshire

This barn conversion is “set to appear on an architecturally focused television programme later this year,” said the agents coyly when it was first listed in early August. They meant Grand Designs, and after it was on the telly viewings leapt by 1,200%. With more than 400 sq m (4,305 sq ft) of space, all the dimensions of this four-bed home are barn-like too, and it comes with a lift for wheelchair access. It is on 1.5 acres with countryside views while Stratford-upon-Avon station is four miles away. £1m. Edwards Exclusive , 01789 611 063
description: The website has revealed the properties that received the most clicks in September
